## Setup
```bash
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install numpy matplotlib pandas loguru
```

## Usage
```bash
# Phase 1 — MPI primitives
python src/hello.py
python src/send_recv.py
python src/bcast_reduce.py

# Phase 2 — distributed matrix multiply
python src/matmul.py

# Phase 3 — scaling benchmark
python src/benchmark.py
```

## Project Structure
```
mpi-matrix-multiply/
├── src/
│   ├── hello.py          # SPMD hello world
│   ├── send_recv.py      # Point-to-point communication
│   ├── bcast_reduce.py   # Broadcast + reduce primitives
│   ├── matmul.py         # Distributed matrix multiply
│   └── benchmark.py      # Strong + weak scaling analysis
├── output/
